Package cz.tomasdvorak.eet.client.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CommunicationException
    Every possible fault caused during communication with EET service.
    CommunicationTimeoutException  
    DataSigningException
    Exception thrown during computation of PKP and BKP security codes.
    DnsLookupFailedException
    DNS lookup failed from some other reason than timeout.
    DnsTimeoutException
    DNS lookup failed after timeout reached.
    InvalidFormatException
    Provided data entry is not in valid format.
    InvalidKeystoreException
    Keystore / Certstore exception thrown, if the application cannot process provided files and their content.
    RequestSerializationException
    Failed to de/serialize EET request from or to String.
    ResponseWithErrorException  
    RevocationListException
    Revocation lists cannot be obtained or processed.
